Backup your settings, select configs and worlds to the cloud. No more re-configuring each one of your instances.

This mod aims to fix probably one of the most annoying things, setting your settings every time you switch computers or instances that uses different folders. It can be best described as a "Steam Cloud" like thing for Minecraft.

**Note**: This mod cannot be used in offline mode!

## Usage Limitations

Every Minecraft account gets 250MB of storage to store their setting and worlds they choose to backup. Due to this you cannot use this mod in offline mod. If you need more storage, consider donating.
